# Sentinel Frontend вЂ” Complete Architecture & Implementation Plan

## Overview

Sentinel is an **AI-powered observability platform with a prompt firewall**. The backend is a fully operational microservices system. This plan defines the complete frontend architecture, tech stack, design philosophy, and page-by-page implementation plan for the Sentinel Dashboard.

---

## Backend State (What's Already Built)

### Available API Endpoints (via Gateway :3000)

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Service | Description |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/users/register` | None | User :4000 | Register new user |
| `POST` | `/users/login` | None | User :4000 | Login в†’ JWT token |
| `GET` | `/users` | Admin | User :4000 | List all users |
| `GET` | `/users/:id` | JWT | User :4000 | Get user by ID |
| `PATCH` | `/users/:id` | JWT | User :4000 | Update user |
| `DELETE` | `/users/:id` | JWT | User :4000 | Delete user |
| `GET` | `/incidents` | JWT | Incident :4001 | Paginated list (filters: status, severity, search) |
| `POST` | `/incidents` | JWT | Incident :4001 | Create manual incident |
| `GET` | `/incidents/:id` | JWT | Incident :4001 | Incident detail + ai_summary |
| `PATCH` | `/incidents/:id` | JWT | Incident :4001 | Update incident |
| `DELETE` | `/incidents/:id` | JWT | Incident :4001 | Delete incident |
| `GET` | `/stats` | None (cached) | Incident :4001 | Dashboard stats |
| `GET` | `/alerts` | JWT | Incident :4001 | Paginated alerts (filters: severity, acknowledged) |
| `GET` | `/alerts/:id` | JWT | Incident :4001 | Alert detail |
| `PATCH` | `/alerts/:id/ack` | JWT | Incident :4001 | Acknowledge alert |
| `GET` | `/audit-logs` | JWT | Audit :4003 | Paginated audit trail |
| `GET` | `/audit-logs/entity/:id` | JWT | Audit :4003 | Audit trail for incident |
| `GET` | `/policy-logs` | JWT | Audit :4003 | Paginated policy violations |
| `POST` | `/firewall/api/ingest` | JWT | Firewall :4002 | Ingest logs (main pipeline) |
| `POST` | `/firewall/api/analyze` | JWT | Firewall :4002 | Direct AI test |
| `GET` | `/firewall/api/policies` | JWT | Firewall :4002 | List knowledge policies |
| `POST` | `/firewall/api/policies` | JWT | Firewall :4002 | Create policy |
| `PATCH` | `/firewall/api/policies/:id` | JWT | Firewall :4002 | Update policy |
| `DELETE` | `/firewall/api/policies/:id` | JWT | Firewall :4002 | Delete policy |
| `GET` | `/projects` | JWT | User :4000 | List projects |

### Stats API Shape (GET /stats)
```json
{
  "incidents": { "total": 150, "open": 42, "inProgress": 18, "resolved": 78, "closed": 12 },
  "severity": { "critical": 8, "high": 31, "medium": 60, "low": 51 },
  "ai": { "analyzedCount": 145, "avgConfidence": 0.847 },
  "alerts": { "total": 38, "unacknowledged": 12 },
  "policyViolations": 89,
  "recentTrend": [{ "date": "2026-04-13", "count": 12 }, ...]
}
```

### WebSocket Events (Socket.io at ws://localhost:3000)
| Client subscribes (emit) | Server emits | Payload |
|---|---|---|
| `subscribe:incidents` в†’ room: `incidents` | `incident:created` | `{ tempId, traceId, source, severity, timestamp }` |
| `subscribe:incidents` | `incident:analyzed` | `{ incidentId, traceId, summary, root_cause, resolution, confidence, analyzedAt }` |
| `subscribe:alerts` в†’ room: `alerts` | `alert:created` | `{ incident_id, traceId, severity, message }` |
| `subscribe:policies` в†’ room: `policies` | `policy:violation` | `{ tempId, traceId, violations[], timestamp }` |

