## System Architecture: Full Stack

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Sentinel Frontend (Next.js)"
        AUTH_PAGE["Login / Register Page"]
        DASH["Dashboard Page"]
        INC_LIST["Incidents List Page"]
        INC_DETAIL["Incident Detail Page"]
        ALERTS_PAGE["Alerts Page"]
        POLICY_PAGE["Policies Page"]
        AUDIT_PAGE["Audit Trail Page"]
        SETTINGS["Settings Page"]

        subgraph "State & Data Layer"
            QUERY["TanStack Query (server state)"]
            ZUSTAND["Zustand (auth + UI state)"]
            SOCKET["Socket.io Client (real-time)"]
        end
    end

    subgraph "Backend (API Gateway :3000)"
        GW["Express + Socket.io"]
        REST["REST API Routes"]
        WS["WebSocket Server"]
    end

    AUTH_PAGE --> ZUSTAND
    DASH --> QUERY
    INC_LIST --> QUERY
    INC_DETAIL --> QUERY
    ALERTS_PAGE --> QUERY
    POLICY_PAGE --> QUERY
    AUDIT_PAGE --> QUERY

    QUERY --> REST
    SOCKET --> WS
    WS --> KAFKA[["Kafka Topics"]]
    REST --> SERVICES[["Microservices"]]
```

